"/rest/api/content/2760147005/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685632513","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632513","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjUxMw==","status":"current","title":"Tpago","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10589376},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632513","tinyui":"/x/AYATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632513","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632513/Tpago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632513"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"cc2c77fd-5c0c-45f2-a972-9e5387cea032\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYLDP/pages/1064304698/Monto+en+los+reintentos+de+pagos+y+d+as+de+cobros+29+30+31\">TPago</a>, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761\" ri:local-id=\"0448ebc4-1c4c-4b5d-a959-e43563341cca\" /></ac:link> y <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"5f0f0f5470b8a90025b61555\" ri:local-id=\"ab5d65cd-b375-4c66-9728-4e75daf60f4a\" /></ac:link>.</p><hr /><h3><strong>Resumen del Cambio en el Proceso de Cobro de Planes</strong></h3><p>Actualmente, Tpago solo permite seleccionar fechas de cobro entre el 1 y el 28 de cada mes debido a la variabilidad en la cantidad de d&iacute;as por mes. Se ha decidido habilitar los d&iacute;as 29, 30 y 31 para dar mayor flexibilidad.</p><p><strong>Nueva regla:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Si la fecha seleccionada no existe en un mes espec&iacute;fico (ejemplo: 31 de febrero), se cobrar&aacute; el &uacute;ltimo d&iacute;a disponible del mes.</p></li><li><p>No se optar&aacute; por cobrar el 1 del mes siguiente para evitar dobles cobros y sobrecarga el d&iacute;a 1.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Ajuste en el proceso:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Se debe validar si el d&iacute;a de ejecuci&oacute;n del proceso es el &uacute;ltimo del mes.</p></li><li><p>Si es el &uacute;ltimo d&iacute;a h&aacute;bil, se encolar&aacute;n los suscriptores con fecha de cobro en los d&iacute;as 29, 30 y 31 para ser procesados ese mismo d&iacute;a.</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Las horas estimadas son: 40</strong></p><hr /><p><strong>Fecha de comienzo</strong>: <time datetime=\"2025-04-23\" /> </p><p><strong>Fecha de entrega: </strong><time datetime=\"2025-04-30\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 441.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 110.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 208.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>Modificaci&oacute;n en m&eacute;todo de retry para enviar amount de link a pay_with_registered_card y agregar par&aacute;metro opcional en dicho m&eacute;todo</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>8</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>Modificaci&oacute;n en procesos de cobro de links para tomar en cuenta dias posteriores al dia de debito si la fecha de hoy es fin de mes</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>24</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"var(--ds-surface, #FFFFFF)\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Code review, deploy a staging, revisi&oacute;n de errores</p></td><td><p>8</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td><p>40</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3754295297"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":91990319},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3754295297/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3754295297/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3754295297/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3754295297/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3754295297","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3754295297/Monto+en+los+reintentos+de+pagos+y+d+as+de+cobros+29+30+31+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3754295297","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3754295297","tinyui":"/x/AQDG3w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}